Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:09.678 --> 00:00:12.471
Hello and welcome to another New York Habitat

00:00:12.471 --> 00:00:14.470
furnished apartment video tour.

00:00:14.470 --> 00:00:16.515
Today we will be giving you a tour

00:00:16.515 --> 00:00:18.055
of a furnished studio apartment

00:00:18.055 --> 00:00:20.096
located on boulevard Bonne Nouvelle.

00:00:20.096 --> 00:00:22.844
This apartment is near the Porte Saint-Denis

00:00:22.844 --> 00:00:24.575
in the 2nd district of Paris,

00:00:24.575 --> 00:00:26.836
where you'll find plenty of shops,

00:00:26.836 --> 00:00:28.442
stores and boutiques.

00:00:50.293 --> 00:00:52.645
This small furnished studio apartment

00:00:52.645 --> 00:00:55.474
is located on the 5th floor (6th floor in the US)

00:00:55.474 --> 00:00:57.934
of a beautiful elevator building.

00:01:06.187 --> 00:01:07.966
The apartment has two glass doors

00:01:07.966 --> 00:01:10.820
that open onto a small charming balcony.

00:01:14.551 --> 00:01:16.345
From the balcony you'll get a view

00:01:16.345 --> 00:01:20.013
of the église Bonne Nouvelle and the Porte Saint Denis.

00:01:25.290 --> 00:01:26.977
The living area of this studio

00:01:26.977 --> 00:01:29.037
is equipped with two sofa beds,

00:01:33.411 --> 00:01:39.506
a table with chairs, a large dresser, and a small TV.

00:01:43.582 --> 00:01:46.171
In the back of the apartment you will find the kitchen.

00:01:47.996 --> 00:01:50.948
This kitchen has a small window and is equipped

00:01:50.948 --> 00:01:53.986
with a sink, a microwave, a dishwasher,

00:01:53.986 --> 00:01:55.172
a washing machine,

00:01:55.172 --> 00:01:57.996
and all of the necessities for cooking.

00:02:00.543 --> 00:02:03.416
The white tiled bathroom is equipped with a shower,

00:02:06.494 --> 00:02:09.208
a sink, and a mirror.

00:02:12.014 --> 00:02:13.374
This apartment is ideal

00:02:13.374 --> 00:02:16.524
for someone looking to stay a few months in Paris.

00:02:17.150 --> 00:02:19.116
Moreover, it makes for a great home base

00:02:19.116 --> 00:02:20.411
in the heart of Paris.

00:02:20.411 --> 00:02:22.859
Now let's go take a look at the neighborhood!

00:02:34.601 --> 00:02:35.805
Coming out of the building

00:02:35.805 --> 00:02:38.081
you are not far from the Porte Saint Denis.

00:02:38.081 --> 00:02:41.525
Built in 1672 at the order of Louis XIV

00:02:41.525 --> 00:02:42.807
in honor of his victories,

00:02:42.807 --> 00:02:44.506
this monumental archway

00:02:44.506 --> 00:02:46.975
replaced a medieval gate in the city walls,

00:02:46.975 --> 00:02:50.683
which they, themselves, date back to the 14th century.

00:02:55.991 --> 00:02:57.254
Near the Porte Saint Denis

00:02:57.254 --> 00:03:00.436
you will find l'église Notre-Dame-de-Bonne-Nouvelle.

00:03:00.436 --> 00:03:02.213
This historic church gives its name

00:03:02.213 --> 00:03:03.234
both to the neighborhood

00:03:03.234 --> 00:03:05.414
and boulevard Bonne-Nouvelle.

00:03:09.151 --> 00:03:12.271
Also located in the neighborhood is Le Grand Rex.

00:03:12.271 --> 00:03:15.427
It is the largest theatre and music venue in Paris.

00:03:15.427 --> 00:03:19.357
The Grand Rex can seat up to 2650 people

00:03:19.357 --> 00:03:21.804
and features the largest screen in Europe.

00:03:21.804 --> 00:03:24.407
This theatre doesn't disappoint.

00:03:25.173 --> 00:03:27.608
As the neighborhood is well known for its textile trade,

00:03:27.608 --> 00:03:29.385
you will find many shops and boutiques

00:03:29.385 --> 00:03:33.105
like in the passages du Caire with its glass rooftop.

00:03:33.435 --> 00:03:34.982
While strolling through the neighborhood,

00:03:34.982 --> 00:03:37.693
be sure to visit rue Montorgueil.

00:03:37.693 --> 00:03:40.503
This well known pedestrian street is always lively

00:03:40.503 --> 00:03:44.058
with its many restaurants, cafés, bakeries and more.

00:03:44.058 --> 00:03:46.381
This is a great place to do your grocery shopping

00:03:46.381 --> 00:03:48.972
to cook in your fully equipped kitchen.

00:03:53.715 --> 00:03:57.585
Be sure to visit our website at nyhabitat.com.

00:03:57.585 --> 00:03:59.504
Here you will find more furnished apartments

00:03:59.504 --> 00:04:01.500
not only in the neighborhood Bonne-Nouvelle,

00:04:01.500 --> 00:04:02.730
but all over Paris.

00:04:02.730 --> 00:04:04.290
Why not rent a furnished apartment

00:04:04.290 --> 00:04:06.433
and live like a true Parisian!

00:04:09.718 --> 00:04:10.779
Well, that's a wrap

00:04:10.779 --> 00:04:13.245
of our furnished apartment video tour today.

00:04:13.245 --> 00:04:14.665
We hope to see you soon

00:04:14.665 --> 00:04:17.582
in the always romantic city of Paris.

